ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectConvention on International Interests in Mobile Equipment and the Protocol to the Convention on International Interests in Mobile Equipment on Matters specific to Aircraft Equipment.
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the CONVENTION on International Interests in Mobile Equipment and the PROTOCOL to the Convention on International Interests in Mobile Equipment on Matters specific to Aircraft Equipment.
